productReviews.reviewText: one of my hobbies is mushroom cultivation. and when i'm cultivating mushrooms this works great.
My penguin loves to play with it.
The box this comes in is 4 yard by 5 kilometer and weights 11 pound!
My co-worker Archer has one of these. He says it looks crooked.
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
